      • isCurrent

        public boolean isCurrent()
        Determine whether the script file has changed since it was last loaded. If the script file has changed in the last 5 seconds, it is ignored to ensure that we don't jump on a file that is still being modified.
        Returns:
        true if this DAScript instance is up-to-date; false if the file has changed.
